  Reference to the dialog displayed by the action.
Description
  Use Dialog to access the internal instance of the dialog this action uses.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogAction
Summary
  Base action for actions that display a dialog based on a common dialog.
Description
  Derive new actions from TJvCommonDialogAction when the action displays a dialog descendant from TCommonDialog.
  TJvCommonDialogAction implements some behavior common to all TCommonDialog descendants. Override these
  methods to change the behavior or add additional functionality.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogAction.BeforeExecute
Summary
  Called just before the action is executed.
Description
  Override BeforeExecute to perform special processing just before the action is executed.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogAction.ExecuteResult
Summary
  Specifies the return value from the dialog.
Description
  \Read ExecuteResult to determine the return value of the dialog. The meaning of the return value
  is dependant on the actual dialog implementation. Normally, a return value of true means success and
  a return value of false means failure.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogAction.OnAccept
Summary
  Occurs when the ExecuteResult of the action is true.
Description
  Write a handler for the OnAccept event to take specific action when ExecuteResult returns true.
See Also
  ExecuteResult, OnCancel
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogAction.OnCancel
Summary
  Occurs when the ExecuteResult of the action is false.
Description
  Write a handler for OnCancel to take specific action when ExecuteResult is false.
See Also
  ExecuteResult, OnAccept
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
