@@TJvCommonDialogFAction
Summary
  Base action for actions that displays a dialog derived from TJvCommonDialogF.
Description
  Derive a new action from TJvCommonDialogFAction when the action should display a dialog
  descendant from TJvCommonDialogF. A TJvCommonDialogF dialog is a dialog component
  that returns a boolean value from it's Execute function.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogFAction.AfterExecute
Summary
  Called after the associated dialog has closed.
Description
  Override AfterExecute to take specific actions when the action has executed it's dialog.
See Also
  BeforeExecute
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogFAction.BeforeExecute
Summary
  Called before the associated dialog is shown.
Description
  Override AfterExecute to take specific actions before the action executes it's dialog.
See Also
  BeforeExecute
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogPAction
Summary
  Base action for actions that displays a dialog derived from TJvCommonDialogP.
Description
  Derive a new action from TJvCommonDialogPAction when the action should display a dialog
  descendant from TJvCommonDialogF. A TJvCommonDialogP dialog is a dialog component
  that has a procedure for it's Execute method (doesn't return a value).
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogPAction.AfterExecute
Summary
  Called after the associated dialog has closed.
Description
  Override AfterExecute to take specific actions when the action has executed it's dialog.
See Also
  BeforeExecute
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCommonDialogPAction.BeforeExecute
Summary
  Called before the associated dialog is shown.
Description
  Override AfterExecute to take specific actions before the action executes it's dialog.
See Also
  BeforeExecute
